{"tid":917021,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[又COMEBACK] TWICE 12月超高速回歸 新曲MV拍攝完成","createTime":"2018-11-26T06:02:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-26T09:37:43.000Z","uid":74065,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"ce8a018a65013b338f6755afda8e1f02dfcf6471","tid":917021,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T06:02:06.000Z","msg":"JYP方面表示 TWICE 年末將發表特別專輯 無放送活動 <br />\n組合TWICE再次回歸<br />\n<br />\n26日，TWICE 所屬JYP娛樂方面表示TWICE將發行特別專輯，會盡快公布具體的日程。<br />\n<br />\n另外，這張專輯是送給粉絲們的禮物，屬於特別專輯性質，因此沒有放送活動。<br />\n<br />\n之前，TWICE在11月5日發行了迷你6輯&lt;YES or YES&gt; 展開了活動。<br />\n<br />\nTWICE將於12月發行repackage專輯,迅速迴歸舞臺.<br />\n<br />\n據多位歌謠界相關人士透露<br />\nTWICE 將在12月發行針對冬季的一首歌曲和特別repackage專輯.<br />\n據悉,爲此TWICE 已於10月末在蒙古祕密拍攝了新曲MV.<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望E份禮物唔洗錢"},{"pid":"5bcddaaec7af8119e147b3bb51e4cee9528f00c7","tid":917021,"uid":152432,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T06:16:11.000Z","msg":"屌又comeback，真係咁驚冇存在感?"},{"pid":"50b75b0a72cc8c9fe6b163bd48b8abe3d8bd5161","tid":917021,"uid":152432,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T06:17:15.000Z","msg":"以前d女團鬥質素<br />\n依家d女團鬥質量"},{"pid":"b94dccc3c073720e889b54d805691b479255b2ef","tid":917021,"uid":74065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5bcddaaec7af8119e147b3bb51e4cee9528f00c7","tid":917021,"uid":152432,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T06:16:11.000Z","msg":"屌又comeback，真係咁驚冇存在感?"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-26T06:17:15.000Z","msg":"佢地應該好驚比IZONE打到起唔到身"},{"pid":"05f2b763cb3789a03591ac5c6e023b51e1f0e151","tid":917021,"uid":152432,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b94dccc3c0